[I] ROCm Tracer Callback/Activity Library for Performance tracing AMD GPUs

[T] ROC-tracer library: Runtimes Generic Callback/Activity APIs. The goal of
[T] the implementation is to provide a generic independent from specific
[T] runtime profiler to trace API and asynchronous activity. The API provides
[T] functionality for registering the runtimes API callbacks and asynchronous
[T] activity records pool support.

